}\par\ltrpar{\langfe1023\alang1023\dbch\af11\dbch\af11\lang1023
A complex sequence of Dcs could be built using special-purpose input tools for constructing them. For instance, purpose-built tools could be provided for constructing a sequence of Dcs representing a mathematical equation, or a sequence of Dcs representing a given time or color.}\par\ltrpar{\langfe1023\alang1023\dbch\af11\dbch\af11\lang1023
