\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
The "Name" column specifies an informative name for the Dc. The names may change in future versions if the current names seem suboptimal. They should not be relied on as unique or stable identifiers. If a name is prefixed with "!", then that Dc is deprecated. Names }{\cs19\i\ai\rtlch \ltrch\loch
should}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
