\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
To learn about how viable and helpful this project would be, I interviewed two people to learn about their use of information technology systems and how they would be affected by the tools proposed here.}
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Interview questions }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  1.\tab}\ilvl0\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx707\li707\ri0\lin707\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
What tasks do you frequently use information technology (IT) systems to complete? A few examples of information technology systems, for purposes of this question, are computers, telephones, portable music players, and fax machines. }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  2.\tab}\ilvl0\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx707\li707\ri0\lin707\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
What aspects of yourself influence your use of, and experience of using, information technology systems? For example, if your job needs you to use IT systems, what is that job and what aspects of it relate to your use of IT systems? Or, if you find IT systems difficult to use because of difficulty processing complex visual stimuli, or because of physical mobility impairments. }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  3.\tab}\ilvl0\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx707\li707\ri0\lin707\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Also, when using information technology systems, are there any other challenges that you face? }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  4.\tab}\ilvl0\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx707\li707\ri0\lin707\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Imagine a computer or smart phone that, when you first start it, presents a list of recent projects you have worked on (such as documents you have had opened), and a list of upcoming projects you have told it about. Would you find a memory aid like that helpful in guiding you to the projects you are there to work on? }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  5.\tab}\ilvl0\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx707\li707\ri0\lin707\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
For the next two questions, imagine an IT system that gives you information about current circumstances \u8212\'97 your name, where you are, the date and year, and recent news and messages. }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  1.\tab}\ilvl1\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx1414\li1414\ri0\lin1414\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
Would that help you feel grounded in the present and more easily able to complete the tasks you are there to work on? }
\par \pard\plain \s24\sb0\sa283{\listtext\pard\plain  2.\tab}\ilvl1\ls18 \li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi-283\tx1414\li1414\ri0\lin1414\rin0\fi-283\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
If you or someone you know has trouble remembering that sort of state information, for instance due to Alzheimer\u8217\'92s disease or dementia, do you think this would be helpful in dealing with that? }
